00:32:59,540 --> 00:33:01,520
 kroz državne obeznice.

342
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:03,380
 I sad je samo pitanje

343
00:33:03,380 --> 00:33:05,460
 da li imate dovoljno kvalitetnih izdavatelja,

344
00:33:05,460 --> 00:33:08,660
 jer narod je prepoznao

345
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:11,620
 da više nisu ovisni

346
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:13,800
 i da moraju držati samo novac u banci,

347
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:15,500
 nego da dio sredstava,

348
00:33:15,500 --> 00:33:16,780
