00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:41,420
 Da, komercijalne banke.

361
00:33:41,420 --> 00:33:42,900
 A zašto bi one to napravili uopće?

362
00:33:42,900 --> 00:33:46,520
 Koja je njihova logika u tom procesu?

363
00:33:46,760 --> 00:33:49,220
 Zato što banke ne mogu funkcionirati

364
00:33:49,220 --> 00:33:50,560
 pri niskoj kamatnoj stopi.

365
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:51,880
 Bankarstvo,

366
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:53,000
 to je ovaj

367
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:55,600
 spuštanje kamatne stope,

368
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:58,160
 posebno na nulu ili negativno,

369
00:33:58,160 --> 00:34:00,920
 u stvari pokazuje koliko je recimo ECB

370
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:03,420
 potpuno izolirano,

371
00:34:03,420 --> 00:34:05,100
 bilo kako je realnosti.

372
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:07,900
 jer vi imate,

373
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:09,760
 recimo da je trošak depozita nula.

374
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:12,240
 Znači neko dođe u banku

375
00:34:12,240 --> 00:34:14,300
 i stavi novac na nula.

376
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:17,660
 Banka ima nekakve svoje,

377
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:19,040
 znači nema troška depozita,

378
00:34:19,040 --> 00:34:20,300
 ali ima svoje troškove.

379
00:34:20,300 --> 00:34:22,560
 Znači mora platiti neke radnike,

380
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:23,800
 prostor, šta god.

381
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:27,260
 Nakon toga ima ono što se zove

382
00:34:27,260 --> 00:34:28,300
 kreditni rizik.

383
