 da kad su kamatne stope ekstremno niske,

402
00:35:07,420 --> 00:35:10,280
 njima je neprofitabilno,

403
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,720
 ne neprofitabilno,

404
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:13,080
 opasno kreditirati.

405
00:35:13,080 --> 00:35:15,280
 Jer

406
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:17,740
 i zbog loših plasmana,

407
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:18,980
 koji su potpuno prirodni,

408
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:20,540
 će imati velike gubitke.

409
00:35:21,200 --> 00:35:22,880
 što se dogodilo u Americi kad je, recimo,

410
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:25,460
 Fed 16. počeo di za kamatno stopo?

411
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:27,120
 Fed počeo di za kamatno stopo,

412
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,480
 investicija je naglo narasla,

413
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:30,460
 kreditiranje je naglo naraslo.

414
00:35:30,460 --> 00:35:33,040
 Zato što su kamatne stope

415
00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:35,060
